Title: Fix saving of help text for auxiliary tags
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: wato
Date: 1678109335
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.3.0b1

If you entered a help text on creation or editing of an auxiliary tag, this
text was not saved and the help input field was empty if you edited this
auxiliary tag again.

